info.description:
Complete API collection for DataMammoth v2. 105 endpoints across 10 modules.

Base URL: {{base_url}}
Auth: Bearer {{api_key}}

All responses follow the v2 envelope format with `meta.request_id` and `meta.version`.
Paginated endpoints support `page`, `per_page`, `sort`, `search`, and `filter[field]` query params.

